00:33.450 --> 00:35.869
Murasaki doesn't do Christmas.

00:35.952 --> 00:37.787
Ho, ho, ho!

00:37.871 --> 00:39.831
- Merry Christmas!
- Santa!

00:41.291 --> 00:43.042
Wait, I can't kiss you.

00:43.126 --> 00:44.210
