- What?

00:55.472 --> 00:57.390
Now it's a party!

00:57.474 --> 00:59.476
Ho, ho, ho.

00:59.559 --> 01:00.769
You ho!

01:00.852 --> 01:02.062
Sonja?

01:04.438 --> 01:05.774
Where's Dong?

01:05.857 --> 01:07.192
How would I know?

01:07.275 --> 01:09.319
He says he's been working late,

01:09.402 --> 01:13.281
and then I found this under his pillow.

01:14.949 --> 01:16.659
- Is that my scrunchie?
- Hey!

01:16.743 --> 01:19.579
You don't barge into people's tugboats...

01:19.662 --> 01:23.833
uh, homes... and wave
a pocket butthole at them!

01:25.001 --> 01:26.544
I put it there, Sonja.

01:27.587 --> 01:29.881
I went to your house
to beg Dong to take me back.

01:29.964 --> 01:32.675
He kicked me out,
but I hid this under his pillow.

01:32.759 --> 01:34.153
I thought, that way,
I might be in his dreams,

01:34.177 --> 01:36.012
like Freddy Krueger, but romantic,

01:36.095 --> 01:37.138
but with the same sweater.

01:37.222 --> 01:39.599
This seems much less
important than my thing.

01:39.682 --> 01:42.519
I'm watching you, Kimmy,
and you never know where I am

01:42.602 --> 01:44.646
because of my invisibility hat.

01:48.566 --> 01:50.568
He kept my scrunchie.

01:50.652 --> 01:52.195
Shut up!

