17:21.248 --> 17:24.084
<i>See, people do the right thing eventually.</i>

17:25.252 --> 17:27.087
I cut that leaf to look like her.

17:28.964 --> 17:31.258
<i>Call us when you can, dear.</i>

17:40.142 --> 17:41.810
