19:08.480 --> 19:10.482
Well, I guess we all have our issues.

19:10.566 --> 19:12.693
But as long as you find the right person,

19:12.776 --> 19:14.611
you know, like Pacey and Joey,

19:14.695 --> 19:16.495
none of the rest of that stuff
really matters.

