20:29.728 --> 20:30.729
Lillian.

20:31.939 --> 20:33.732
Kimmy.

20:33.815 --> 20:35.359
My loyal servants.

20:36.652 --> 20:38.987
You know what?

20:39.071 --> 20:40.239
