20:57.547 --> 20:59.549
Let me see if I can figure it out.

21:06.640 --> 21:08.475
I blame my mom for this.

21:08.558 --> 21:11.061
She never taught me
about the birds and the bees.

21:11.144 --> 21:12.562
And the Durnsville school system

21:12.646 --> 21:14.606
only taught us
about the birds and the bees.

21:17.317 --> 21:19.194
Did you know God won't let penguins fly

21:19.278 --> 21:20.696
because they're gay?

21:27.202 --> 21:29.288
Ready for the hurricane?

21:29.371 --> 21:32.457
Uh, Kimmy?

21:32.541 --> 21:34.334
Oh, no!

21:34.418 --> 21:35.978
Have I been punching you
this whole time

21:36.003 --> 21:37.087
and didn't realize it?

21:37.170 --> 21:39.131
I think I have a latex allergy.

21:39.214 --> 21:42.134
This happened once before
when I tried to sleep

21:42.217 --> 21:44.386
on a pile of cut-up bike tires.

21:44.469 --> 21:46.555
Call back.

21:46.638 --> 21:48.140
And now I can't breathe,

21:48.223 --> 21:51.351
which means my brain isn't getting

21:51.435 --> 21:53.645
any of your emails, Peter.

21:57.232 --> 21:58.150
No!

21:58.233 --> 21:59.568
Not <i>My Girl.</i>

21:59.651 --> 22:01.820
It's supposed to be <i>Dawson's Creek.</i>

22:06.241 --> 22:07.576
Hello, 911, this is Kimmy.

22:07.659 --> 22:09.161
How are you?

22:09.244 --> 22:10.404
I'm just trying to be polite.

22:10.454 --> 22:11.747
