23:06.843 --> 23:08.154
All right, just take the painting

23:08.178 --> 23:09.596
directly to the granddaughter,

23:09.679 --> 23:12.432
Maya Wiener-Hertz-Allott-Cozzabudts.

23:12.516 --> 23:13.683
All right, let's go.

23:13.767 --> 23:16.978
I got to wheels up back to D.C.
in 90 minutes.

23:17.062 --> 23:18.772
He has a jet?

23:18.855 --> 23:22.067
