24:09.322 --> 24:12.659
You know, there's no
old telephones in here.

24:12.742 --> 24:15.078
- Uh-huh.
- And you're in handcuffs...

24:15.162 --> 24:17.914
which is making my brain feel calm

24:17.998 --> 24:19.833
for more totally normal reasons.

24:19.916 --> 24:21.501
Kimmy, are you sure?

24:21.585 --> 24:23.378
We're never going to see each other again,

24:23.461 --> 24:25.797
and it's really gross back here.

24:26.882 --> 24:28.717
